        <figcaption>7月21日上午，习近平乘坐飞机抵达林芝米林机场，西藏各族干部群众载歌载舞，欢迎习近平的到来。（新华社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs5cbazg1f6ww0pd9k.jpg?rh9MHlBe5HBJrr5Idi0jBO2HUcn8.Sc3&itok=aWhQj1zK" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>7月21日下午，习近平在林芝市巴宜区林芝镇嘎拉村村民达瓦坚参家仔细察看储藏室。（新华社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs5cbrj7snxodg5lro.jpg?MAuzLZGCRo2dMsI3bBf99d1TkSE9zu9i&itok=ICUsiFEe" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>7月22日上午，习近平（右三）乘坐专列实地察看拉林铁路沿线建设情况，深入研究有关问题。（新华社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs5dp49rxh1k68med9k.jpg?VdusYPDXT9yvA7QgDvPIFhxhPfQxs6O0&itok=M7z7itNW" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>7月22日下午，习近平在位于拉萨西郊的哲蚌寺察看措钦大殿。（新华社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs3ojiel3nki8a5id4.jpg?9f4yafzQSDNilgc4BRqVwFKN7Q7zl59x&itok=BjiAFhy1" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>7月22日下午，习近平在布达拉宫广场考察时，向游客和当地群众挥手致意。（新华社）</figcaption></figure><figure class="image-placeholder "><img alt class src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/inline_medium/public/2021-07/file7gs5cc9asdv5uehul1f.jpg?C8c3QhAepnhGDcsmiQztfkqPg7svUx6Z&itok=D_F3YZ7U" pinger-seen="true" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
        <figcaption>7月22日下午，习近平在考察位于拉萨市老城区的八廓街时，向各族群众挥手致意。（新华社）</figcaption></figure>
